outputs.output_descr: The project aims to support disadvantaged women and their families through providing them with economic and social services, psychosocial support, recreational  and awareness raising interventions. The project is considered high priority for Gazan women and their families.The project contributes to empower women in Gaza through enhancing women's skills in organizing, addressing their own problems and increasing income. The outcome of the project is the improvement of access to social and economic services for women and their families in Nuseirat and Jabalia. It will be achieved through the training of women in Jabalia and Nuseirat in providing sustainable social and economic services.

project_descr: Empowering Disadvantaged Women and their families in Emergency and Post - Crisis Situations, the output is Women in Jabalia and Nuseirat are trained in providing sustainable social and economic services.
